  <brief_title>A Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of ETC-1002 in Subjects With Elevated Blood Cholesterol and Either Normal or Elevated Triglycerides</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Placebo-Controlled, Randomized, Double-Blind, Parallel Group, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of ETC-1002 in Subjects With Hypercholesterolemia and Either Normal or Elevated Triglycerides.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
