  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This Phase 2 proof-of-concept study will assess the lipid regulating efficacy and safety of
      ETC-1002 in subjects with hypercholesterolemia and either normal or elevated triglycerides.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
